- Oh. Easy, here.

01:27:31.811 --> 01:27:34.466
The doctor said
if it hurts to push this.

01:27:34.640 --> 01:27:36.381
And it'll release
more painkillers.

01:27:41.952 --> 01:27:42.996
That better?

01:27:46.783 --> 01:27:48.828
