01:27:53.964 --> 01:27:55.966
How long have I...

01:27:56.140 --> 01:27:57.359
- Couple of days.

01:28:00.100 --> 01:28:01.972
Oh no, don't worry.

01:28:02.146 --> 01:28:03.452
It was treatable.

01:28:06.846 --> 01:28:07.804
Yeah.

01:28:09.806 --> 01:28:11.938
Another day or so,
and we can go home.

01:28:14.724 --> 01:28:16.291
